rComments: Amazing professor that is very passionate for her job as a teacher. Always gives quick responses and is pretty reasonable with requests.

I took the course for BR2 and she is a really nice prof! She replies to emails quickly and answers all kinds of questions with patience! A very enthusiastic lecturer. However, she is quite a tough grader.

She was so easy to talk to outside of class and through emails (there was one time I emailed her at midnight and she emailed back at 12:03) and readily gave extensions and guidance. She also gave us pep talks during the year. But she's a tough grader, tends to ramble, and doesn't always leave time for a break.
